data.description: STOP THE SEARCH!!! We have found the home for you!  This beautifully maintained 3-bedroom, single level ranch in Howland is everything that you have been looking for and an entertainers dream with room for all functions and gatherings! This home features a large living room that flows into the kitchen and dining room adjacent!  This home also features a walkout basement directly to an inground pool with a beautiful view of the river from the backyard! This view will have you dreaming of summer! But don't worry as winters will not be a bother when you are lounging in this large living room with water views and a cozy wood fireplace to keep you warm as you relax from a long day of work makes this the embodiment of firelit living!  The Heat pumps and wood stove make for fantastic alternate heat options during the winter and the heat pumps provide AC throughout those warm summer months. Public boat access is just roughly half a  mile up the road. Just a short interstate drive to Bangor and close to multiple lakes and ponds make this home an extremely desirable location!  Call today!
